{
  "id": "sys-03-outbound-lead-outreach",
  "name": "SYS 02 — Outbound Lead Outreach Sequence",
  "description": "Multi-touch outbound sequence triggered by webhook at /enroll-outreach (e.g. when a lead is enrolled from SYS 01 — Lead Sourcing Machine, SYS 01 — AI Voice Lead Qualification, or SYS 01 — Website Form Lead Intake). Sends Touch 1 email, waits per CONFIG, Touch 2 email, optional SMS touches; uses owner/company from CONFIG and logs each touch to the Automations Log.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## SYS 02 — Outbound Lead Outreach Sequence\n\n**Trigger:** Webhook POST at `/enroll-outreach` (e.g. when a lead is enrolled from **SYS 01 — Lead Sourcing Machine**, **SYS 01 — AI Voice Lead Qualification**, or **SYS 01 — Website Form Lead Intake** after a HubSpot form submission).\n\n**What it does:** Runs a multi-touch sequence: Touch 1 email (intro), then waits CONFIG's follow-up delay; Touch 2 email (value); optional Touch 3 SMS. All messaging uses owner and company info from CONFIG. Logs each touch to the Automations Log.\n\n**Dependencies:** CONFIG, Send Email, Send SMS, Log. Update HubSpot outreach/replied flags as needed.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "note-sys03",
      "name": "Note — About this workflow",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        80,
        80
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "enroll-outreach",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "sys03-trigger",
      "name": "Outreach Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        250,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "source": "database",
        "workflowId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "1eTTVoSFSlSPvZV4",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "workflowInputs": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {},
          "matchingColumns": [],
          "schema": [],
          "attemptToConvertTypes": false,
          "convertFieldsToString": true
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "sys03-config",
      "name": "Get Config",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.executeWorkflow",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        470,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const raw = $('Outreach Webhook').first().json;\nconst input = raw && raw.body && typeof raw.body === 'object' && !Array.isArray(raw.body) ? raw.body : raw;\nconst config = $('Get Config').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    contactId: input.contactId || input.contact_id || '',\n    company: input.company || '',\n    industry: input.industry || '',\n    firstName: input.firstName || input.firstname || '',\n    config: config\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "sys03-prepare",
      "name": "Prepare Sequence Data",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        690,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const data = $('Prepare Sequence Data').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    to: data.config.owner.email,\n    subject: `Quick question about ${data.company}'s operations`,\n    html: `<p>Hi ${data.firstName || 'there'},</p><p>I came across ${data.company} and wanted to reach out. We help ${data.industry || 'businesses'} like yours automate operations — everything from lead follow-up to invoicing to client onboarding.</p><p>Most of our clients save 15-20 hours per week once their systems are running.</p><p>Worth a 15-minute conversation to see if there's a fit?</p><p>— John<br/>IntraWeb Technologies</p>`,\n    workflowName: 'SYS 02 — Outbound Lead Outreach Sequence'\n  }\n}];"
      },
