        "jsCode": "const data = $('Prepare Sequence Data').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    to: data.config.owner.email,\n    subject: `What ${data.industry || 'business'} owners are automating in 2025`,\n    html: `<p>Hi ${data.firstName || 'there'},</p><p>Quick follow-up — I've been working with several ${data.industry || 'businesses'} on automating their operations this year.</p><p>The pattern I keep seeing: owners spending 10+ hours/week on tasks that should take zero. Follow-ups that slip through the cracks. Invoices that go unpaid because nobody sent a reminder.</p><p>We build systems that handle all of it — automatically. No templates, no generic software. Custom-built for your operation.</p><p>Here's my calendar if you want to see what this looks like for ${data.company}: ${data.config.owner.calendarLink}</p><p>— John</p>`,\n    workflowName: 'SYS 02 — Outbound Lead Outreach Sequence'\n  }\n}];"
